Our statistical model is formulated as follows for ΔT; an identical and independent model is used for %ΔP. The estimate of future change in mean temperature between t = 0 and t = 1, υ1, is based on historical observed temperature change to t = 0, ΔX0:1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
